Explaination for items
We will use a Pixelblaze for the coding, which most of the coding is already done, it's just that we need a connection and to map out all the LEDs for it.
The battery will supply the power obviously
The 5V battery regulator will limit the batteries output to not overpower the items
The circuit board is to connect all the wires and LEDs together onto a panel.
The wires.
Tweezers to plant each LED
The soldering iron to keep the leds in place
The reflow oven to make sure the connection still works.
